										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/markets/shares-trading" target="_blank" rel="noopener">美國股市</a>週四走高，但未能突破近期的歷史高點。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-41821" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SP-500-–-Daily-Chart-1.png" alt="SP 500 – Daily Chart" width="967" height="588" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SP-500-–-Daily-Chart-1.png 967w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SP-500-–-Daily-Chart-1-300x182.png 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/SP-500-–-Daily-Chart-1-768x467.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 967px) 100vw, 967px" /></p>
